<div id="pf4b6e" class="pf w9c h337" data-page-no="4b6e"><div class="pc pc4b6e w9c h337"><div class="t m7e9 x3 h5 y40a ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Northern European Division Thanks God for You. </div><div class="t ma45 x3d h35 ybd9 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">In 1981, when Sabbath Schools </div><div class="t mf4d x3 h35 y11d0 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">worldwide last focused attention on Northern Europe, we told you of our plans for an </div><div class="t me3d x3 h35 y40c ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">evangelistic center in Poland, a school above the Arctic Circle in Norway, and a new building </div><div class="t m115e x3 h35 y2ea ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">for Toivonlinnan Junior College in Finland. Of the $1,582,888.30 you gave that thirteenth </div><div class="t md25 x3 h35 y66e ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Sabbath, 25 percent ($395,722.07) was shared among the three projects. Because of </div><div class="t mc9 x3 h35 yabc ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">difficulties in obtaining materials, the building in Poland was delayed, but construction has </div><div class="t m650 x3 h35 y1206 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">begun on the college building in Finland, and the school building in north Norway (pictured </div><div class="t m172f x3 h35 yb87 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">above) is already in use. These children express the appreciation we all feel. </div><div class="t m412 x27 h35 y78a ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The Special Projects portion of this quarter&apos;s offering on June 30 will be divided between </div><div class="t ma31 x3 h35 y359 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">library extension at Newbold College in England and the construction of an evangelistic center </div><div class="t m1bde x3 h35 yafd ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">in Eindhoven in the southern Netherlands. Thank you again for your prayers and generosity on </div><div class="t m192c x3 h35 y9a7 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">our behalf. </div><div class="t m37 x16 h35 y8dd ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Walter R. L. Scragg, President, Northern European Division </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
